'''第47屆[[日間時段艾美獎|日間時段艾美獎]]'''（{{lang-en|47th Daytime Emmy Awards}}）由[[美國|美國]][[國家電視藝術與科學學院|國家電視藝術與科學學院]]主辦，獎勵2019年在日間時段播出的優秀電視節目。國家電視藝術與科學學院原本打算於6月12－14日在[[加州|加州]][[帕薩迪納_(加利福尼亞州)|帕薩迪納]]市政禮堂<ref name="deadline20191024">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/daytime-emmys-expanding-three-nights-2020-1202768153/|title=Daytime Emmys Expanding To Three Nights For 2020 Awards|first=Erik|last=Pedersen|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|publisher=|location=|date=2019-10-24|accessdate=2020-01-06|author=|work=|language=en|format=|trans-title=|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212014324/https://deadline.com/2019/10/daytime-emmys-expanding-three-nights-2020-1202768153/|dead-url=no}}</ref>連續三個晚上舉行頒獎典禮<ref>{{cite news|title=Daytime Emmy Awards Will Expand to Three Nights in 2020|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/daytime-emmy-awards-2020-dates-june-1203382121/|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]|date=2019-10-24|accessdate=2020-01-06|author=|work=|language=en|format=|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212014305/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/daytime-emmy-awards-2020-dates-june-1203382121/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但所有相關活動最終都因[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]而取消。最後，頒獎典禮以視像直播形式於6月26日舉行，並取消所有相關公眾活動。此次典禮於[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS電視網]]播映，自2015年改為以[[串流媒體|串流媒體]]播放以來首次於美國電視台播放，亦是繼2011年後再次於[[廣播網|廣播網]]播映典禮<ref name="deadline20200520">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2020/05/daytime-emmy-awards-2020-cbs-date-schedule-1202939440/|title=Daytime Emmys To Air Live Virtual Ceremony On CBS In June; Nominations Coming Thursday|first=Patrick|last=Hipes|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|publisher=|location=|date=2020-05-20|accessdate=2020-05-20|author=|work=|language=en|format=|archive-date=2021-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327142347/https://deadline.com/2020/05/daytime-emmy-awards-2020-cbs-date-schedule-1202939440/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

入圍名單原定於2020年4月27日公佈<ref name="NATAS Dates">{{cite web|title=47th Daytime Emmys Rules|url=https://daytimeemmys.dmds.com/Content/documents/GeneralRulesandProcedures.pdf|accessdate=2020-01-06|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[國家電視藝術與科學學院|國家電視藝術與科學學院]]|language=en|location=|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630035349/https://daytimeemmys.dmds.com/Content/documents/GeneralRulesandProcedures.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但同樣受疫情影響而延至5月21日<ref name="deadline20200520" />。

== 典禮 ==
本屆日間時段艾美獎原訂首次連續三個晚上舉辦頒獎典禮，取代原本分開舉行的主要獎項典禮及{{link-en|創意藝術獎|Creative Arts Emmy Award}}典禮<ref name="deadline20191024" />。2020年3月19日，國家電視藝術與科學學院宣布由於[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]而將頒獎典禮延期舉行<ref>{{cite web|title=Work on 47th Annual Daytime Emmy Awards Will Continue, Despite Postponement|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/03/47th-annual-daytime-emmy-awards-postponed-1202219232/|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-03-19|format=|publisher=|language=en|website=indiewire.com|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226085413/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/03/47th-annual-daytime-emmy-awards-postponed-1202219232/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Daytime Emmys Postponed|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/daytime-emmys-postponed-response-coronavirus-1285538|accessdate=|author=|date=March 19, 2020|format=|publisher=[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]|language=en|website=|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225023448/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/daytime-emmys-postponed-response-coronavirus-1285538|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於4月28日公佈將實體典禮改為透過視像形式舉行，但仍未公佈實際典禮日期<ref>{{cite web|title=Daytime, Sports and News & Doc Emmys to Be Handed Out in "Virtual" Ceremonies|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/daytime-sports-news-doc-emmys-presented-virtual-ceremonies-1292404|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-04-29|format=|publisher=[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]|language=en|website=|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212014328/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/daytime-sports-news-doc-emmys-presented-virtual-ceremonies-1292404|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月20日，正式公佈頒獎典禮將於6月26日於[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS電視網]]播映，並在翌日於該台的[[脫口秀|脫口秀]]《{{link-en|談話|The Talk (talk show)}}》公佈入圍名單<ref name="deadline20200520" />。

視像典禮上僅頒發了主要獎項，部分獎項在典禮舉行的同時在日間時段艾美獎的官方推特上公佈；而餘下的獎項則預定在7月公佈，[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]獎項的獲獎者亦未於典禮上公佈<ref name="deadline20200520" />。 6月18日，主辦方宣佈典禮的特備節目將由《{{link-en|談話|The Talk (talk show)}}》負責主持<ref>{{Cite web|title=Daytime Emmys 2020 to be Hosted by the Stars of CBS’ ‘The Talk’|url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/daytime-emmys-hosts-cbs-the-talk-2020-1234641717/|accessdate=2020-06-22|author=|date=2020-06-18|last=Schneider|first=Michael|format=|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303033836/https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/daytime-emmys-hosts-cbs-the-talk-2020-1234641717/|archive-date=2021-03-03|access-date=|website=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 獎項變更 ===
國家電視藝術與科學學院決定將{{link-en|最佳年輕男演員獎|Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Younger Actor in a Drama Series}}及{{link-en|最佳年輕女演員獎|Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Younger Actress in a Drama Series}}合併為[[性別中立|性別中立]]的「最佳年輕演員獎」，以達致其有關[[性別認同|性別認同]]的目標<ref>{{cite news|title=Daytime Emmys Combine Young Performer Categories, Clarify Gender Identity Rules|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/daytime-emmys-rules-gender-young-performer-categories-2020-1203388913/|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]|date=2019-10-31|accessdate=2020-01-06|author=|work=|language=en|format=|archive-date=2019-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105032637/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/daytime-emmys-rules-gender-young-performer-categories-2020-1203388913/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

